videos.headline: Duke's Stinson weaves through traffic for 94-yard kick-return TD
videos.description: Jaylen Stinson takes the kickoff all the way to the end zone for Duke's first touchdown of the game against Miami.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Duke’s Stinson weaves through traffic for 94-yard kick-return TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Miami's Restrepo is open in the end zone for 24-yard TD
videos.description: Xavier Restrepo hauls in a nice throw from Tyler Van Dyke to pull Miami even with Duke with a 24-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Miami’s Restrepo is open in the end zone for 24-yard TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Miami's Rambo makes a 12-yard TD catch under pressure
videos.description: Charleston Rambo beats his Duke defender into the end zone for a 12-yard touchdown in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Miami’s Rambo makes a 12-yard TD catch under pressure) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jaylan Knighton's 2-yard TD extends Miami's lead
videos.description: Jaylan Knighton plunges up the middle for a Hurricanes touchdown against Duke.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jaylan Knighton’s 2-yard TD extends Miami’s lead) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rambo manages to hold on for his 2nd TD of the day
videos.description: With the sun in his eyes, Charleston Rambo reels in a tough catch under pressure from Tyler Van Dyke in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rambo manages to hold on for his 2nd TD of the day) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Miami puts another score on the board with a 9-yard strike
videos.description: Thaddius Franklin Jr. powers his way through Duke's defense for a 9-yard touchdown to extend Miami's big lead.
